<title>USA: FemRx given FDA clearance for PEARL.</title>
<headline>FemRx given FDA clearance for PEARL.</headline>
<dateline>SUNNYVALE, Calif 1997-04-28</dateline>
<text>
<p>FemRx Inc on Monday said it received marketing clearance from the U.S. Food and Drug Administration for its Physiologic Endometrial Ablation/Resection Loop, known as PEARL.</p>
<p>The company believes the technology eliminates the most serious risks associated with operative hysteroscopy.</p>
<p>FemRx expects to begin product shipments incorporating PEARL in the fourth quarter of 1997.</p>
